{"tid":1327930,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[影片]花小小時間認識自己嘅香港史","createTime":"2019-07-17T18:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:59:03.000Z","uid":157522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a399281ef5fb829803b9878c130dd3280c2a57","tid":1327930,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fMriboCeUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3fMriboCeUs&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQso26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=671c2fd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fMriboCeUs</a><br />\n1990年，鄧小平接見李嘉誠，重申一貫立場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「不會變，不可能變，不是說短期不變，是長期不變，這個道理我過去講過多少次」<br />\n「就是說五十年不變，五十年之後更沒有變的道理」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇到好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本香港一個咁有特色嘅地方<br />\n回歸後就統一赤化<br />\n仲要好多時候係衰係班賣港賊手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db73c8eda8f5e26dd1f3b8a7023aba9d0152b1ce","tid":1327930,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:59:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fc10170943cc5a6f57845f3d800fdc45e3ae69f","tid":1327930,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6a5f57817f85c61fbe7c4a4b7e3d20544cf853e","tid":1327930,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc10170943cc5a6f57845f3d800fdc45e3ae69f","tid":1327930,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"中国人最終想統一全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fad05